Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.23,0:22:32.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}时光的流逝 今日的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:36.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}也理所当然地到来了
