Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}心中却深知再也没有「再见」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:47.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}人生地疏的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:50.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}我们在此相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:57.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}不知何时 微风在身边刮起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:03.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}但我并不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:06.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}我只能尽力去传达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:13.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}每当迷茫 困惑 受伤之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:17.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}双手之间满载的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:22.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}朝向指尖微微流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:27.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(1830,540)}请紧紧握住那双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:18.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}なくしたもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:22.10,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}大切なこと 守れなかった僕らの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:25.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}笑顔の影　この先いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:29.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}晴れること祈ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.23,0:22:32.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}時間は過ぎ　今日の終りは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:36.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}当たり前にやってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:39.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}「じゃあまたね」と見送る背中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.97,0:22:43.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}本当は「また」なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.81,0:22:47.01,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}誰かの知らない街
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:50.76,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}僕らはそこで出会って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:57.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}いつからか風は　いつもそこにふいてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:03.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}でも僕は君じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:06.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}伝えることしか出来なくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:13.51,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}迷い戸惑い傷を受けたり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:17.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6\pos(110,540)}二つの手に乗せた记忆
